commit_message:
Merge pull request #2 from nikostr/qc

Fix QC issues
add diff report for integration test
set all wrapper versions to v0.75.0
Updates mapping test for bwa v1
Adds bwa-mem2 index test, updates bwa index test
Adds basic support for bwa-mem2 using temporary wrapper
Updates integration test action to use singularity, mamba
Fixes compliance with snakemake workflow catalog
Adds snakemake linting and integration test action
Removes old keep functionality, updates tests
Adds tests for deepvariant, faidx, samtools merge
Adds tests for bwa index, mapping and ensembl genome fetching
Ignores glnexus db, does cmp as fallback comparison in VcfGzChecker
Adds deepvariant html and multiqc as parts of report
Updates documentation to reflect sample renaming
Replaces sample removal with sample renaming
Updates mapping to use new wrapper
Updates joint calling code to comply with schema
Updates joint_calling_groups schema, adds sample tsv files
Moves bam indexing into bam merging
Makes bcf sample merging a config issue, removes old bcf merging logic
Adds code to merge joint calling groups, and comments on how to handle this. Should remove this later, better to let users specify in joint_calling_groups.tsv
Some placeholder wrappers added, minor bugfixes
Improves formatting, adds --force-samples option to bcftools merge
Replaces query with loc, fixing error
Fixes bugs, removes gatk pipeline reference
Adds code for handling units file, updates schemas
Adds input to rule all, updates qc steps
Updates calling rules to new mapping output
Adds support for multiple read sets per sample, bam merging
Adds support for single-end trimming, references dna-seq-gatk-variant-calling-pipeline
Adds units schema, updates samples schema
Adds vcf merging and syncs joint_calling_groups naming
Adds schemas for samples and joint calling group sheets
Adds support for joint calling, with glnexus placeholder
Adds previous work to cookiecutter template
